text: This is the web version of the WSJ’s daily economic newsletter. You can sign up for daily delivery here. Good morning. In today’s issue, a crucial week in trade looms, the meaning of the latest GDP report, Sprint and T-Mobile test Trump’s antitrust policy, and the dollar’s long decline reverses.
